description:
Recorded on 3.09.20 wayyyy before the panic shopping and when toilet paper was still available.

Bobby is human Prozac. Bert blames Hitler. Koloko lives with a petri dish. We talk the molly incident, rotten lemons, 50 Cent memes, enema virginity, and once again promise to do the Malibu Triathlon.
